Package it.polimi.se2019.model.cards

Class Move

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.model.cards.Move
  • public class Move
extends java.lang.Object
    Supports a subAction in an effect that allows the movement of player(s). It handles the player to move using objectToMove and targetSource. It handles the destination tiles using targetDestination.
